{"tid":1821210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外國巴打展覽緊，點解無人捐？（歐洲巡迴展眾籌）","createTime":"2020-01-12T05:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T16:30:49.000Z","uid":76310,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a04f12197b2108cb96809af11cf552a9efafc3bb","tid":1821210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:52:16.000Z","msg":"眾籌網址 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Ffree-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=a9587afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition</a><br />\n<br />\n各位手足，我哋係Free Hong Kong Exhibition團隊，由一班海外香港人組成，主要打國際戰線。我哋希望以巡迴展覧嘅形式，將香港人嘅聲音帶到海外。作為响城牆外面生活嘅人，我哋自覺有責任將港共政府嘅所作所為話俾全世界知。响西方民主社會，人民就係力量，政府嘅決策同立法往往都以民意為依歸，而展覽正正可以提供一個空間同平台，直接同市民接觸交流。我哋希望以普羅大眾為出發點，提高民間對香港事態嘅關注，團結國際民運陣線，希望响國際間有更加多迴響，間接向港共政府施壓。<br />\n<br />\n好耐都未夠數<br />\n外國巴打努力緊 <br />\n岩岩仲比中共打壓烏克蘭展覽<br />\n麻煩大家幫手捐一捐"},{"pid":"ac81848d03ebb1b4fb00e353511de430a8c4cc39","tid":1821210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbffd1c6318d4da824fa46af3c2ace58883130f","tid":1821210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f347ee983e633d8f0715d09783807ca9cce8419d","tid":1821210,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T06:57:53.000Z","msg":